+./scripts/bootstrap_home_miner.sh
+```
+
+**Outcome:** ✅ PASS
+
+**Evidence:**
+```
+[INFO] Stopping Zend Home Miner Daemon
+[INFO] Starting Zend Home Miner Daemon on 127.0.0.1:8080...
